<ab><expan>Arnolt<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>,
                                <expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan> zu Uffenheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>erbott<ex>en</ex></expan> habt, ob die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        die strassen für Uffenheim gen Frankenfurt auf oder ab faren
                                <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan>, so woltet ir sie von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des <expan>pfallnczgraf<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> sicher geleyten etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und danken <add>des</add>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleiss. Also
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir das <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>kawfflewt<ex>en</ex></expan> und den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>zu wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> tun; und wurd uns
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> icht zu <expan>synne<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        das <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewch
                            <expan>verkünd<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und getrawen ewch wol, ob die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ewr <expan>yend<ex>er</ex>t</expan>
<expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wurd<ex>en</ex></expan>, ir wellet in umb
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Anthonii.</ab>
</div>
